# 🏗️ Global College LMS — Implementation Plan

> **Approach:** Build incrementally from existing Replit code. No restart from scratch.  
> **Rule:** Ask user before moving to each new phase.  
> **ORM:** Drizzle ORM (keep existing) | **IDs:** Integer (keep existing)  
> **Structure:** Restructure to `client/` + `server/` clean layout  

