## Phase 5: Branch & User Management

> **Goal:** Admin can manage branches, students, teachers

| # | Task | Details |
|---|------|---------|
| 5.1 | Branch CRUD API | GET (public), GET/POST/PUT/PATCH (admin) with student count |
| 5.2 | Branch management frontend | Admin branches page with add/edit/deactivate |
| 5.3 | Student management API | GET list (paginated, searchable), GET detail, PUT edit, DELETE, reset password |
| 5.4 | Student management frontend | Admin students page with table, search, filters, detail view |
| 5.5 | Teacher management API | GET list, POST create (email creds), GET detail, PUT edit, DELETE |
| 5.6 | Teacher management frontend | Admin teachers page with create modal, table, detail view |
| 5.7 | Update registration | Add branch dropdown (fetched from API), validate branch selection |

**Checkpoint:** ✅ Admin can manage all users and branches

