## Phase 6: Course System

> **Goal:** Full course CRUD with sections, lessons, teacher course builder

| # | Task | Details |
|---|------|---------|
| 6.1 | Course CRUD API (admin) | Create, edit, approve, reject, archive, delete courses |
| 6.2 | Course CRUD API (teacher) | Create draft, edit own, submit for approval |
| 6.3 | Section CRUD API | Create, edit, delete, reorder sections within course |
| 6.4 | Lesson CRUD API | Create, edit, delete lessons within section, PDF upload |
| 6.5 | Course catalog API (public) | List LIVE courses with filters, search, pagination |
| 6.6 | Course detail API (public) | Single course with sections, lessons, teacher info |
| 6.7 | Teacher course builder page | Course info form + sections/lessons builder + submit for approval |
| 6.8 | Admin course management page | Table with status filters, approve/reject actions |
| 6.9 | Admin course review page | Full preview + approve/reject with notes |
| 6.10 | Public course catalog page | Search, filter, sort, pagination, course cards |
| 6.11 | Public course detail page | Description, syllabus accordion, teacher card, enroll button |

**Checkpoint:** ✅ Full course lifecycle works: create → review → publish → browse

