## Phase 8: Video Learning System

| # | Task | Details |
|---|------|---------|
| 8.1 | AES-256 encryption service | Encrypt/decrypt YouTube video IDs |
| 8.2 | Stream token endpoint | `/student/lessons/:id/stream-token` → verify enrollment, return signed JWT |
| 8.3 | Embed endpoint | `/student/lessons/:id/embed` → validate token, return youtube-nocookie URL |
| 8.4 | Video access logging | Log every access with userId, lessonId, IP, userAgent |
| 8.5 | Progress tracking API | PATCH `/lessons/:id/progress` → upsert watchedPercent, check completion |
| 8.6 | Course completion service | When all lessons complete → mark enrollment complete |
| 8.7 | Video player component | Sandboxed iframe, overlay protection, right-click block, YouTube IFrame API |
| 8.8 | Lesson viewer page | Two-panel layout: sidebar timeline + video player + tabs (PDF, Discussion) |

**Checkpoint:** ✅ Students can watch protected videos with progress tracking

