## Working Rules

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Ask before moving to next phase** — user confirms completion
> 2. **Copy existing code** — don't rewrite from scratch if it works
> 3. **Test each phase** — verify functionality before proceeding
> 4. **One phase at a time** — no jumping ahead
> 5. **Commit-worthy chunks** — each task should be a logical unit

